citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T02:51:10.000Z","msg":"東張西望 搵吳幸美再試食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f4b5501d65acaaedc8b3df1d5529b845ae1b04","tid":46792,"uid":7582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T02:54:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161004/19790324\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161004%2F19790324&d=DLcSJ3at4d3q9zJfdG0PmXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=6d41ef9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161004%2F19790324&h=7b9c81fd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161004/19790324</a><br />\n<br />\n熱狗藏208隻蟻　OK罰款<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】OK便利店售賣的即食熱狗，今年1月被顧客發現有208隻蟻，顧客向食環署舉報。食環署事後票控OK便利店一項食物品質與購買人要求不符罪，公司代表昨在東區法院承認控罪，被判罰款3,500元。<br />\nOK便利店承認於今年1月23日，在香港仔華富邨華富商業中心分店售賣的「超級熱狗──『湯種』熱狗包」上，有208隻蟻亞科成蟲，違反《公眾衞生及市政條例》第52（1）條。<br />\n辯方求情指，OK便利店事後已作跟進清潔，拆開機器檢查亦發現不到有蟻。特委裁判官林希維指，今次已是OK便利店第7次犯案，而且蟻數量多，蟻雖然很細小，「但一隻都嫌多」，敦促OK便利店做好監察工作。OK便利店過往有6次相同罪名的案底，對上一次罰款5,000元，本案的華富邨分店則是初犯。<br />\n案件編號：ESS24982/16<br />\n■記者伍嘉豪"},{"pid":"2410f3861fb89d5e43cb284cb6daf775bde0a420","tid":46792,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T03:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9d88b05574565df620fed30fed6f0502df58b5","tid":46792,"uid":32531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T03:06:12.000Z","msg":"咁都照食？同港豬有咩分別"},{"pid":"45c25372ae2190f02c956fcd1f9128decc0be3a7","tid":46792,"uid":8748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T03:07:04.000Z","msg":"記者朋友做嘢喇喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96735bc1933f87c3572d8800e97980519930b8b2","tid":46792,"uid"